import React from 'react'; const Subscriptions = () => (

Choose Your Plan

Select the membership plan that suits your needs.

{/* Basic Plan */}
Basic Plan

₹2799/year

✓ Unlimited Notifications

✓ Email Alerts

Priority Support

Unlimited Tender Filing

No-cost Consultancy

{/* Pro Plan */}
Pro Plan

₹5899/year

✓ Unlimited Notifications

✓ Email & SMS Alerts

✓ Priority Support

✓ 1 Tender Filing

No-cost Consultancy

{/* Enterprise Plan */}
Enterprise Plan

₹14999/year

✓ Unlimited Notifications

✓ Email, SMS & Phone Alerts

✓ AI Based Bid Support

✓ 3 Tender Filing

✓ No-Cost Consultation

); export default Subscriptions;
